  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_051_00003",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "他既不能老是表示姑息，",
    "pause_ms": 250
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_051_00004",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "又不能像在加利福尼亚旅行期间那样处处迁就她了。",
    "pause_ms": 600
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_051_00005",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "她本想不露声色，",
    "pause_ms": 250
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_051_00006",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "免得惹人注意，",
    "pause_ms": 250
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_051_00007",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "殊不知反而显出她对“热情支持繁荣戈镇运动”丝毫不感兴趣。",
    "pause_ms": 600
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_051_00008",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "对于这个运动，",
    "pause_ms": 250
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_051_00009",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "肯尼科特倒是深信无疑，",
    "pause_ms": 250
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_051_00010",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "所以要求她对建设“白光大街”和新的工厂表示热情关注。",
    "pause_ms": 600
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_051_00011",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "他说：",
    "pause_ms": 250
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_051_00012",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "“老实说，",
    "pause_ms": 250
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_051_00013",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "我已然尽到自己最大的努力了，",
    "pause_ms": 250
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_051_00014",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "现下就指望你了。",
    "pause_ms": 600
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_051_00015",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "多少年来，",
    "pause_ms": 250
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_051_00016",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "你一直在嘀嘀咕咕，",
    "pause_ms": 250
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_051_00017",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "埋怨我们这儿死气沉沉。",
    "pause_ms": 600
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_051_00018",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "现下布劳塞一到这里，",
    "pause_ms": 250
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_051_00019",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "群情激奋，",
    "pause_ms": 250
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_051_00020",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "就像你一直梦寐以求的目标那样要把戈镇美化一番，",
    "pause_ms": 250
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_051_00021",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "嘿，",
    "pause_ms": 250
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_051_00022",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "你却说他是个大老粗，",
    "pause_ms": 250
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_051_00023",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "你偏偏连接送乐队的卡车都不肯坐上去。",
    "pause_ms": 600
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_051_00024",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "” } {",
    "pause_ms": 1000
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_051_00025",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "卡萝尔心里正在纳闷：",
    "pause_ms": 250
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_051_00026",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "“真不知道他的这种论点是从哪一篇社论里看来的？",
    "pause_ms": 600
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_051_00027",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "”于是，",
    "pause_ms": 250
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_051_00028",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "她就抗议说，",
    "pause_ms": 250
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_051_00029",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "“你听着，",
    "pause_ms": 250
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_051_00030",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "亲爱的，",
    "pause_ms": 250
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_051_00031",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "为什么你们这些保守派不可以光明正大地向他宣战呢？",
    "pause_ms": 600
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_051_00032",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "你们之所以反对这位发起人，",
    "pause_ms": 250
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_051_00033",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "并不是你们认为他在煽动民心，",
    "pause_ms": 250
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_051_00034",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "而是害怕他把那些农场主联合起来，",
    "pause_ms": 250
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_051_00035",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "不让你们镇上这些人通过承接抵押、",
    "pause_ms": 250
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_051_00036",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "收购小麦和开店经商等方式牟取暴利。",
    "pause_ms": 600
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_051_00037",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "当然咯，",
    "pause_ms": 250
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_051_00038",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "这会儿正赶上我们跟德国作战，",
    "pause_ms": 250
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_051_00039",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "但凡我们不喜欢的事，",
    "pause_ms": 250
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_051_00040",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "不管是商业上的竞争也好，",
    "pause_ms": 250
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_051_00041",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "还是低级的音乐也好，",
    "pause_ms": 250
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_051_00042",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "我们都可以给它扣上一顶‘亲德’的帽子。",
    "pause_ms": 600
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_051_00043",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "要是我们这会儿在跟英国作战，",
    "pause_ms": 250
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_051_00044",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "我说，",
    "pause_ms": 250
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_051_00045",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "你们也会管那些激进派叫‘亲英派’的。",
    "pause_ms": 600
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_051_00046",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "等到战争一结束，",
    "pause_ms": 250
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_051_00047",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "我想你们又要管他们叫‘赤色无政府主义者’吧。",
    "pause_ms": 600
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_051_00048",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "这是古已有之的一种绝招，",
    "pause_ms": 250
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_051_00049",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "可以随心所欲地给我们的反对派横加罪名！",
    "pause_ms": 600
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_051_00050",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "反正金钱万能，",
    "pause_ms": 250
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_051_00051",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "我们总是巴不得金钱落进自己的腰包里。",
    "pause_ms": 600
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_051_00052",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "所以，",
    "pause_ms": 250
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_051_00053",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "当我们竭尽全力不让他们夺走的时候，",
    "pause_ms": 250
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_051_00054",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "常常认为自己是得到上帝的恩准的。",
    "pause_ms": 600
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_051_00055",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "不论教会也好，",
    "pause_ms": 250
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_051_00056",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "还是政治演说家也好，",
    "pause_ms": 250
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_051_00057",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "他们始终是这样认为的。",
    "pause_ms": 600
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_051_00058",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "我想，",
    "pause_ms": 250
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_051_00059",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "当我管博加特太太叫‘清教徒’，",
    "pause_ms": 250
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_051_00060",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "管斯托博迪先生叫‘资本家’的时候，",
    "pause_ms": 250
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_051_00061",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "我常常也是这样认为的。",
    "pause_ms": 600
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_051_00062",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "不过，",
    "pause_ms": 250
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_051_00063",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "你们做买卖的人，",
    "pause_ms": 250
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_051_00064",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "由于你们都是天真无邪、",
    "pause_ms": 250
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_051_00065",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "精力充沛而又浮夸自负，",
    "pause_ms": 250
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_051_00066",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "管保叫我们望尘莫及——”\n卡萝尔要讲的话儿远远还没有完，",
    "pause_ms": 250
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_051_00067",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "无奈肯尼科特也顾不上像往日里那样对她相敬如宾，",
