  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_051_00069",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "“住嘴！",
    "pause_ms": 600
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_051_00070",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "你这一套我可听腻了！",
    "pause_ms": 600
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_051_00071",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "你嘲笑我们戈镇，",
    "pause_ms": 250
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_051_00072",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "说它有多么寒碜，",
    "pause_ms": 250
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_051_00073",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "多么沉闷，",
    "pause_ms": 250
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_051_00074",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "我一直都忍着不说。",
    "pause_ms": 600
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_051_00075",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "你瞧不起一大拨像萨姆那样的好人，",
    "pause_ms": 250
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_051_00076",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "我也随你高兴去吧。",
    "pause_ms": 600
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_051_00077",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "甚至于你在挖苦我们眼看着热情支持繁荣戈镇运动的时候，",
    "pause_ms": 250
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_051_00078",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "我也都撒手不管你。",
    "pause_ms": 600
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_051_00079",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "可是有一件事儿叫我实在难以容忍，",
    "pause_ms": 250
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_051_00080",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "那就是说，",
    "pause_ms": 250
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_051_00081",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "我可不能让自己的太太也到处去煽动别人。",
    "pause_ms": 600
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_051_00082",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "尽管你说话时可以吞吞吐吐，",
    "pause_ms": 250
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_051_00083",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "躲躲闪闪，",
    "pause_ms": 250
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_051_00084",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "可你是知道得很清楚的，",
    "pause_ms": 250
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_051_00085",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "正如你所说的那些激进派都是反战的。",
    "pause_ms": 600
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_051_00086",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "那么，",
    "pause_ms": 250
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_051_00087",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "现在就让我开门见山地正告你：",
