  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_051_00089",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "要找碴子，",
    "pause_ms": 250
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_051_00090",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "发牢骚，",
    "pause_ms": 250
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_051_00091",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "尽管请便吧，",
    "pause_ms": 250
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_051_00092",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "不过以后我们还是要把这些家伙都给抓起来的。",
    "pause_ms": 600
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_051_00093",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "要是他们这些人连一点儿爱国心也没有，",
    "pause_ms": 250
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_051_00094",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "我们还得教育他们要爱家乡、",
    "pause_ms": 250
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_051_00095",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "爱国家。",
    "pause_ms": 600
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_051_00096",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "真是天知道，",
    "pause_ms": 250
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_051_00097",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "我一辈子都没想到：",
    "pause_ms": 250
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_051_00098",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "这样的大道理我还得向自己的太太念叨，",
    "pause_ms": 250
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_051_00099",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "不过话又说回来，",
    "pause_ms": 250
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_051_00100",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "你要是继续给那些家伙撑腰，",
    "pause_ms": 250
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_051_00101",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "那就别怪我们对你不客气了！",
    "pause_ms": 600
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_051_00102",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "还有一件事儿，",
    "pause_ms": 250
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_051_00103",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "我说你也许还会哗啦哗啦乱讲什么要求言论自由！",
    "pause_ms": 600
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_051_00104",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "哼，",
    "pause_ms": 250
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_051_00105",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "什么言论自由不自由！",
    "pause_ms": 600
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_051_00106",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "我说我们这儿自由多得实在数不过来了，",
    "pause_ms": 250
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_051_00107",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "什么言论自由啦，",
    "pause_ms": 250
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_051_00108",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "什么煤气自由啦，",
    "pause_ms": 250
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_051_00109",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "什么啤酒自由啦，",
    "pause_ms": 250
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_051_00110",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "什么恋爱自由啦，",
    "pause_ms": 250
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_051_00111",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "还有，",
    "pause_ms": 250
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_051_00112",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "你那开口闭口净是该死的自由啦。",
    "pause_ms": 600
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_051_00113",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "要是按着我的想法办，",
    "pause_ms": 250
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_051_00114",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "我一定要让你们这些人规规矩矩地过日子，",
    "pause_ms": 250
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_051_00115",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "哪怕是我真的不得不把你抓了起来——”\n“威尔！",
    "pause_ms": 600
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_051_00116",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "”现在她几乎一点儿都不胆怯了，",
    "pause_ms": 250
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_051_00117",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "“依你看来，",
    "pause_ms": 250
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_051_00118",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "我要是听了‘诚实的吉姆·布劳塞’的讲话没有像大家那样如痴似醉，",
    "pause_ms": 250
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_051_00119",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "难道说也算是‘亲德’派吗？",
    "pause_ms": 600
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_051_00120",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "依你看来，",
    "pause_ms": 250
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_051_00121",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "是要让我循规蹈矩做一个好太太吧！",
    "pause_ms": 600
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_051_00122",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "”\n他嘴里还在咕噜咕噜地发牢骚说：",
    "pause_ms": 250
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_051_00123",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "“你刚才说的这些话跟你平日里的批评，",
    "pause_ms": 250
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_051_00124",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "一听就合辙。",
    "pause_ms": 600
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_051_00125",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "本来我早就该知道，",
    "pause_ms": 250
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_051_00126",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "凡是有益于戈镇的事情，",
    "pause_ms": 250
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_051_00127",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "你都会表示反对——”\n“你可说得很对。",
    "pause_ms": 600
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_051_00128",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "我所做的一切，",
    "pause_ms": 250
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_051_00129",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "都是始终如一的。",
    "pause_ms": 600
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_051_00130",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "我并不是属于戈镇的。",
    "pause_ms": 600
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_051_00131",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "我之所以这么说，",
    "pause_ms": 250
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_051_00132",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "并不意味着戈镇的过错，",
    "pause_ms": 250
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_051_00133",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "说不定还是我自己的过错。",
    "pause_ms": 600
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_051_00134",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "好吧！",
    "pause_ms": 600
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_051_00135",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "反正对我来说都是一个样！",
    "pause_ms": 600
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_051_00136",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "既然我在这里不得其所，",
    "pause_ms": 250
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_051_00137",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "那我索性离开就得了。",
    "pause_ms": 600
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_051_00138",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "我再也不用问你答应不答应了。",
    "pause_ms": 600
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_051_00139",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "我说什么也得走了。",
    "pause_ms": 600
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_051_00140",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "”\n他嘟嘟囔囔地说着：",
    "pause_ms": 250
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_051_00141",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "“要是不叫你太为难的话，",
    "pause_ms": 250
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_051_00142",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "请你告诉我，",
    "pause_ms": 250
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_051_00143",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "你打算离开这里多久？",
    "pause_ms": 600
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_051_00144",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "”\n“我也不知道。",
    "pause_ms": 600
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_051_00145",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "也许是一年，",
    "pause_ms": 250
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_051_00146",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "也许就是一辈子吧。",
    "pause_ms": 600
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_051_00147",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "”",
    "pause_ms": 1000
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_051_00148",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "“我明白了。",
    "pause_ms": 600
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_051_00149",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "当然咯，",
    "pause_ms": 250
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_051_00150",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "我也是很乐意干脆把诊所卖了，",
    "pause_ms": 250
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_051_00151",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "陪着你到处跑呢。",
    "pause_ms": 600
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_051_00152",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "你乐意让我跟着你一块儿去巴黎学艺术，",
    "pause_ms": 250
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_051_00153",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "那时候，",
    "pause_ms": 250
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_051_00154",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "也许我身上穿着棉绒裤子，",
    "pause_ms": 250
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_051_00155",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "头上戴着女人的无边小帽，",
    "pause_ms": 250
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_051_00156",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "吃意大利细条实心面过日子？",
    "pause_ms": 600
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_051_00157",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "”\n“不，",
    "pause_ms": 250
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_051_00158",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "我想大可不必麻烦你了。",
    "pause_ms": 600
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_051_00159",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "你到现在还不十分了解我。",
    "pause_ms": 600
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_051_00160",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "我马上就要走了——真的我要走了——而且是单独一个人走！",
    "pause_ms": 600
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_051_00161",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "我得去找自己合意的工作做——”\n“找工作做？",
    "pause_ms": 600
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_051_00162",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "找工作做？",
    "pause_ms": 600
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_051_00163",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "当然咯，",
    "pause_ms": 250
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_051_00164",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "这可没有错！",
    "pause_ms": 600
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_051_00165",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "不过你的问题就出在这里啊！",
    "pause_ms": 600
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_051_00166",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "原来是你工作太少，",
    "pause_ms": 250
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_051_00167",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "闲得发慌呢。",
    "pause_ms": 600
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_051_00168",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "你要是身边有五个孩子，",
    "pause_ms": 250
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_051_00169",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "又没有雇女用人，",
    "pause_ms": 250
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_051_00170",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "而且还得像那些农妇既要干家务，",
    "pause_ms": 250
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_051_00171",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "又要忙着撇奶油，",
    "pause_ms": 250
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_051_00172",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "那么，",
    "pause_ms": 250
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_051_00173",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "你也就不至于会如此不知足了。",
    "pause_ms": 600
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_051_00174",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "”\n“我知道。",
    "pause_ms": 600
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_051_00175",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "人们——不分男女——就像你那一号人十之八九都会这样说的。",
    "pause_ms": 600
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_051_00176",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "他们对我的所作所为就是有这么个看法。",
    "pause_ms": 600
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_051_00177",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "反正我不打算跟他们争辩。",
    "pause_ms": 600
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_051_00178",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "那些生意人每天七个钟头坐在公事房吹牛说大话，",
    "pause_ms": 250
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_051_00179",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "却轻描淡写地要我生一打十二个孩子。",
    "pause_ms": 600
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_051_00180",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "事实上，",
    "pause_ms": 250
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_051_00181",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "像那样的生活我不是也都照样过吗？",
    "pause_ms": 600
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_051_00182",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "我们三天两头雇不到用人，",
    "pause_ms": 250
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_051_00183",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "所有的家务还不是由我自己料理？",
    "pause_ms": 600
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_051_00184",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "此外，",
    "pause_ms": 250
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_051_00185",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "我还要照看休，",
    "pause_ms": 250
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_051_00186",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "又要去红十字会工作，",
    "pause_ms": 250
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_051_00187",
    "type": "narration",
    "speaker": "narrator",
    "gender": "unknown",
    "content": "而且也都做得头头是道。",
    "pause_ms": 600
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "Chapter_051_00188",
    "type": "narration",
